flowRoot.flowPara: Deckahedron World marries deck-building, worker-placement, and set-collection mechanisms of modern board games with the innovation blossoming in indie role-playing games like FATE and Apocalypse World.
It's is a game about a party of fate-tempting adventurers becoming champions of their own Hero's Journey, in the dangerous kingdoms of a swords-and-magic fantasy realm.
The Hero's Journey story structure is written into the campaign rules
Born as a hack of Dungeon World aimed to encourage faster, lighter, improvisational play
